    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T07.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Oh?"
    
    "And?\""
    
    "\"And?---you....\""
    
    "I swallow hard."
    
    "She stares right at me."
    
    "Almost---a stare which says she will attack me immediately if I move even the slightest bit."
    
    "\"Is---isn't it strange, Arcueid?"
    
    "Nrvnqsr is dead."
    
    "So why are these incidents still happening?"
    
    "Don't tell me, that, you---\""
    
