    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T03.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"That's not it at all."
    
    "That's not me, but another vampire.\""
    
    "Arcueid responds immediately, loosening the tension."
    
    "But I'm not satisfied."
    
    "\"What do you mean?"
    
    "The work of another vampire?"
    
    "So they just keep coming?\""
    
