    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T01B.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Of course not."
    
    "The serial killings were always the work of just one vampire from the very beginning."
    
    "So no new vampires will come, and Nrvnqsr was unrelated to those incidents.\""
    
    "----Eh?"
    
    "Nrvnqsr was, unrelated....?"
    
    "\"Wha---what do you mean?\""
    
    "\"It's just like I said."
    
    ".... You're normally pretty sharp, but you're lost at some points."
    
    "Think back, Shiki."
    
    "Nrvnqsr was a vampire, but did he ever suck human blood?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_29B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "\"Suck blood?"
    
    "He ate humans and---oh.\""
    
    "I see."
    
    "Why didn't I notice such a simple mistake?"
    
    "The victims of the serial killings are found with their bodies drained of blood."
    
    "But Nrvnqsr was different."
    
    "He didn't leave any dead bodies behind."
    
    "He not only drank the blood, but also ate the meat, leaving no trace."
    
    "To prove it, the people eaten by him in the hotel were treated as missing people, not killed people."
    
    "So---that means, it is something completely different."
    
    "\"Wait."
    
    "Then what is the serial killing going on right now?"
    
    "Just who is doing it?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_29B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T03.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"That's a different vampire than Nrvnqsr."
    
    "To be more specific, that vampire is why I came here, and Nrvnqsr came here following me."
    
    "It's that sort of correlation.\""
    
    "\"---Wha.. So the one you're after wasn't Nrvnqsr after all....!?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_29B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T01A.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
